        result: "<p>The random question from a complete stranger puzzles the sentient, but they shake off the confusion and point to the torch grass growing nearby. They pluck a stalk that’s already fading, leaving the still-growing plants to flourish. Gain flora <span class='card-num'>1060</span>.</p>"
