        result: "<p>The Traveler gathers their thoughts. “We were a small crew on a terraforming vessel, leading the way for a colony ship. The chrono technology was still in the experimental stage—you will discover it in another 100 years or so. It mostly worked as intended: We arrived at a barren planet, jumped back in time a few hundred million years, seeded the planet with the origins of life, then jumped forward to see the results. Sometime during that final jump the chrono tech failed, and most of the crew died in the crash. I was the lone survivor, though only thanks to the ship’s life support system. My brain and body remain inside the ship, with this hologram free to roam the world.” Gain 3 boost and destiny <span class='card-num'>1608</span> (place it in the center).</p>"
