        result: "<p>To your surprise, someone yells back. “What’s the future like?” they ask. You describe your surroundings, and after a few seconds, they make an offer. If you toss some coins through the rift, they will invest the money in real estate that should gain great dividends in the future, which they will stash under the bridge. Do you accept?</p><details><summary>yes (pay between $1 and $10)</summary><div><p>roll a skill die. If it’s <span class='engage skill'>engage</span>, triple your investment. If it’s <span class='take skill'>take</span>, lose your investment. For any other roll, double your investment.</p></div></details><details><summary>no</summary><div><p>Gain 1 morale.</p></div></details>"
