        result: "<p>You hear rumors of a dragon living in a mountain just north of the windswept grasslands. You also learn that not all elder dragons are old—legend tells of a special egg that, when hatched, will bring a new elder dragon into this world. Gain the Map of Caves (<span class='card-num'>1252</span>), and each player gains 1 random skill.</p>"
