        result: "<p>Several meters underground, you feel a sense of satisfaction and strength. Gain 1 health and 1 boost. You may either stop or continue with an <span class='overpower skill'>overpower-<svg class='◊' viewBox='0 0 500 500'><use href='#i-cost-2'/></svg>-<span class='action'>DIG</span></span> action to go deeper (then read the next result):</p><details><summary><svg class='◊' viewbox='0 0 500 500'><use href='#i-dig' /></svg> Continue</summary><div><p>A solid material halts your progress, and you excavate a large crystal. Gain item <span class='card-num'>1163</span>.</p></div></details>"
