        action: "<span class='overpower'>FORCE</span> the lock",
        result: "<p>After great resistance, the lock snaps open. Roll 4 skill dice; you may reroll each die once. If you have at least 3 of a kind, gain item <span class='card-num'>1189</span>. Instead, if you have at least one pair, gain item <span class='card-num'>1162</span>. Otherwise, gain $4.</p>"
